हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/Z3RbBX
show.description: Sinful Ties is a dark romantic drama filled with betrayal, family pressure, and dangerous love. The story follows Shruti Khurana, a young woman forced into an arranged marriage with Karan Mehra, an arrogant and controlling man. Trapped between her family's rigid expectations and Karan’s abusive behavior, Shruti finds herself in a suffocating world where love is a weapon and trust is a gamble.
